track_notes: Start layby A5, walk along road to footpath sign up track SH 690 602. Care around buildings SH 697 603 to find correct track. Pick up track into corrie SH SH 701 605. You may have to climb gate if locked. Onto open hillside, no path. Arrive summit. Either return same way, or continue to NW-002. Note, continuing to NW-002 there is one steep ridge descent off Pen yr Helgi Du and small rock step on Craig yr Ysfa.
Space for one car at start. Can be boggy if there has been heavy rainfall. Well defined track.
Two pounds parking at Gwern Gof Isaf campsite on A5 - see my track for NW-002 for more info

Total time (including ops): 5hr 55m. Maximum difficulty: Swiss Alpine Club Grade T2. Uncurated GPX which may contain navigation errors, detours and hazards. Additional route information may be available at www.m1hax.uk. Track data by Richard M1HAX licensed under Creative Commons BY-NC-SA.
